828
00:44:51,359 --> 00:44:52,228
- Oh yeah?

829
00:44:52,262 --> 00:44:53,096
You got a car yet?

830
00:44:54,313 --> 00:44:58,588
- Just don't go anywhere okay, like, wait just a minute.

