833
00:45:04,914 --> 00:45:06,930
- Yes everything's all taken care of Mrs. Carver.

834
00:45:06,964 --> 00:45:07,937
- Okay.

835
00:45:07,972 --> 00:45:09,954
- Um do you want me to carry that for you.

836
00:45:09,988 --> 00:45:12,629
- No, no, no you've got another customer.

837
00:45:12,664 --> 00:45:14,854
- She's a special one.

