00:45:14,889 --> 00:45:15,758
- Bye.

839
00:45:15,792 --> 00:45:16,696
- Thank you.

840
00:45:18,573 --> 00:45:20,554
- I can't find my ticket.

841
00:45:20,589 --> 00:45:23,543
- No problem, I have the authority to have it totally

842
00:45:23,577 --> 00:45:25,247
taken care of.

843
00:45:25,281 --> 00:45:26,811
Just sign here.

844
00:45:28,931 --> 00:45:31,502
And you can put down your ring size too

845
00:45:31,537 --> 00:45:33,970
because you know I might be wanting to put a deposit

