847
00:45:34,909 --> 00:45:36,612
- Now slow down Billy.

848
00:45:36,646 --> 00:45:39,324
Winning my heart is not like playing a lottery ticket.

849
00:45:39,358 --> 00:45:41,477
- I know, I know, I'm fully aware.

850
00:45:41,513 --> 00:45:45,198
A job, a car, a proposal.

851
00:45:45,232 --> 00:45:46,517
