852
00:45:46,552 --> 00:45:48,742
we got rules you know,

853
00:45:48,776 --> 00:45:50,306
we got some structure you know.

854
00:45:50,342 --> 00:45:51,488
It's all good.

855
00:45:51,522 --> 00:45:54,650
In fact I, I gotta document it.

856
00:45:56,423 --> 00:45:58,474
Relax, it's mine.

857
00:46:00,802 --> 00:46:03,132
(clicking)

858
00:46:11,265 --> 00:46:13,141
- Hey, hey, hey Billy, Billy.

859
00:46:14,254 --> 00:46:16,721
