- [Woman] Where do you think you're going?

876
00:47:25,088 --> 00:47:27,765
(phone ringing)

877
00:47:36,107 --> 00:47:37,740
- Hello?

878
00:47:37,774 --> 00:47:39,061
- Hey hon.

879
00:47:39,096 --> 00:47:40,694
- Hey.

880
00:47:40,729 --> 00:47:43,232
- Hey the New York trip is back on the books again.

881
00:47:43,267 --> 00:47:45,109
Jeff and I are on the four o'clock.

882
00:47:45,144 --> 00:47:47,089
I'll be back Friday late okay?

883
00:47:47,125 --> 00:47:47,993
(giggling)

884
00:47:48,028 --> 00:47:48,584
- Sure.

885
00:47:48,619 --> 00:47:49,592
Where are you?

886
00:47:49,626 --> 00:47:52,199
It sounds like you're having a good time.

887
00:47:52,234 --> 00:47:53,902
- Just leaving a boring business lunch.

888
00:47:53,937 --> 00:47:55,258
I'm calling you tonight.

889
00:47:55,293 --> 00:47:56,023
Kiss Stella.

890
00:47:57,100 --> 00:47:59,776
(phone beeps)

891
00:48:05,789 --> 00:48:07,006
- [Woman] We don't wanna be late.

892
00:48:10,655 --> 00:48:12,914
