00:48:15,694 --> 00:48:17,884
- Mommy, when's daddy coming home?

894
00:48:17,919 --> 00:48:19,275
- I don't know.

895
00:48:21,534 --> 00:48:22,541
- Does he know?

896
00:48:22,576 --> 00:48:23,793
- Well I'm not sure.

897
00:48:25,530 --> 00:48:28,311
- So, nobody knows.

898
00:48:31,821 --> 00:48:34,985
- Yeah, I'm sorry Stella but nobody does know.

899
00:48:40,406 --> 00:48:43,465
(kettle whistling)

