00:52:22,365 --> 00:52:24,763
- Hey the church looks terrific.

981
00:52:24,798 --> 00:52:30,081
- Well congratulations and don't forget to breathe, okay.

982
00:52:30,116 --> 00:52:30,984
Oh.

983
00:52:32,341 --> 00:52:33,348
Hi sweetie.

984
00:52:34,494 --> 00:52:36,789
- Thank you for everything.

985
00:52:36,824 --> 00:52:38,422
- Well you are welcome.

986
00:52:39,499 --> 00:52:40,405
Bye.

