1225
01:05:56,894 --> 01:05:59,120
or if he went out there and diverted it with his tractor

1226
01:05:59,154 --> 01:06:01,274
as Joan claims he did.

1227
01:06:01,309 --> 01:06:02,838
- I never touched that creek.

1228
01:06:02,873 --> 01:06:03,846
